    <h1>Tables</h1>
    <p>Tables are the best way to present data, but the default values are not pretty. Furatto takes care of that by pulishing the default styling and taking it to the next level.</p>

    <div class="row">
      <h4><em>Building the markup</em></h4>
      <p>The markup to build a table on Furatto is really simple, actually you don't have to do anything else if you already implement them on your site.</p>
